               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">The names, Gäbrä Ḥǝywät and ʾAmätä Mikaʾel, are written in the supplication formulas at the beginning (fol. 5ra) and the end of the Vita (fols. 43rb, 43vb). Additionally, names of the members of his family are listed: Wäldä Maryam (his father), Wälättä Libanos (his mother) (fols. 5ra, 43rb, 43vb) and 10 names of his brothers and sisters (fol. 43rb). They were added later in a smaller script, in the main hand.</persName>
